			<div class="container">
				<div class="columns sixteen">
					<div class="vrg_nav-logo">
						<span class="vrg-icon">j</span>
					</div>
					<ul>
						<li id="nav_whatwedo"><a href="#">What We Do</a></li>
						<li id="nav_aboutus"><a href="#">About Us</a></li>
						<li id="nav_ourwork"><a href="#">Our Work</a></li>
						<li id="nav_contact" class="last"><a href="#">Contact us</a></li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</nav>
		<section class="vrg_whatwedo" id="whatwedo">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="columns sixteen">
					<h2 class="textCentered heading">What We Do</h2>
					<div class="columns nine">
						<p>We help you build that positive experience right into your product. We provide creative services for multiple facets of the digital industry from mobile applications to web applications.</p>
<p>Reaching out to your potential customers is harder then it has ever been. We help you plan out your strategy to <span class="italic">attack</span>  from all flanks.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		<section class="vrg_aboutus" id="aboutus">
			<div class="arrowLeft"><%= image_tag("arrowLeft.svg", :class =>  "svg") %></div>
			<div class="container">
				<div class="columns sixteen">
					<h2 class="textCentered heading">About Us</h2>
				</div>
				<ul>
					<li id="1">
						<div class="columns sixteen brokenheartBackground">
							<div class="brokenheartHeart animated pulse"></div>
							<div class="columns nine">
								<h3 class="bold">No More Broken Hearts</h3>
								<p>What sets one designer or developer apart from the rest? We have chosen to deliver amazement, joy and craft, embraced by distinctive creativity.</p>
								<p>You ask for the goods. We deliver the great. We are committed to exceeding your expectations, but not your budget.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li id="2">
						<div class="columns sixteen">

							<div class="columns nine">
								<h3 class="bold">Creative Machines</h3>
								<p>At VRG, we are less creative machines, and more creative producers of machinations, but in the nicest possible sense.</p>
								<p> We scheme and conspire together, to design and devise intriguing strategies for our clients, and ultimately for their global user base. We <span class="italic">love</span> what we do!</p>
							</div>
							<div class="columns six creativemachinesBackground">
								<div class="creativemachinesPulley1 animated rotateCW"></div>
								<div class="creativemachinesPulley2 animated rotateCW"></div>
								<div class="bubbles">
									<div class="bubble1 animated animated.bubble1 fadeOutUp infinite"></div>
									<div class="bubble2 animated fadeOutUp infinite"></div>
									<div class="bubble3 animated animated.bubble3 fadeOutUp infinite"></div>
									<div class="bubble4 animated animated.bubble4 fadeOutUp infinite"></div>
									<div class="bubble5 animated animated.bubble5 fadeOutUp infinite"></div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li id="3">
						<div class="columns nine">
							<h3 class="bold">Storytellers</h3>
							<p>Each story becomes a part of history. VRG's creations each tell a story of art borne from need, climaxing with flair and imagining.</p>
							<p>Our client accolades and user experiences spur us on to even greater and higher plains of conceptual form. Let our next story become a part of your history.</p>
						</div>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="arrowRight"><%= image_tag("arrowRight.svg", :class =>  "svg") %></div>
		</section>
